# usr/

User-facing documentation for Intent, organized as task-oriented guides and reference materials. Contains installation instructions, workflow guidance, command references, and best practices for LLM collaboration.

## Files

- `user_guide.md` -- Task-oriented guide covering installation, getting started, steel threads, documentation management, LLM collaboration, and common workflows
- `reference_guide.md` -- Complete reference for commands, document templates, directory structure, configuration options, and terminology
- `deployment_guide.md` -- Installation methods, configuration, integration, maintenance, upgrading, and troubleshooting for various environments
